---
type Props = {
  variant?: 'home' | 'about';
};

const { variant = 'home' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`brenda section brenda-${variant}`}>
  <div class="container brenda-grid">
    <div class="brenda-image" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 250" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
        <rect width="200" height="250" fill="#efc6b9" />
        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="40" fill="#d28b75" />
        <path d="M40 230 Q100 160 160 230" fill="#d28b75" />
        <text x="100" y="245" text-anchor="middle" font-family="serif" font-size="10" fill="#3a3a3a">Brenda, portrait coming soon</text>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="brenda-text">
      <p class="eyebrow">The artist</p>
      <h2>Built to be the part you remember.</h2>
      <p>
        Brenda is the artist behind every Balloonia install. What drives her is simple: the piece you book today should be the one you and your guests still talk about years from now. The arch in the photo on your mantle. The backdrop your kid still remembers from their fifth birthday. The detail that turns the day into something worth keeping.
      </p>
      {variant === 'home' && (
        <p>
          <a class="brenda-link" href="/about">Read Brenda's story →</a>
        </p>
      )}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .brenda-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-7);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .brenda-image {
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--color-paper-edge);
  }
  .brenda-image svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }
  .brenda-text h2 {
    max-width: 22ch;
  }
  .brenda-text p {
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    font-size: var(--font-size-lg);
    line-height: var(--line-relaxed);
  }
  .brenda-link {
    color: var(--color-accent-deep);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 4px;
  }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .brenda-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.4fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }
  }
</style>
